text: Sharan Wheelock is an Australian water polo player. She competed for the Australian women's national water polo team in the 1998 World Aquatics Championships, 1991 FINA Women's Water Polo World Cup, 1995 FINA Women's Water Polo World Cup, and 1997 FINA Women's Water Polo World Cup. == References == Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Australian water polo players
